t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"jump-to-nav\" class=\"mw-jump\">\n\t\t\t\t\tJump to:\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#mw-head\">navigation</a>, \t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#p-search\">search</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"mw-content-text\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\" class=\"mw-content-ltr\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div style=\"border: 1px solid #33FF66; background-color: #e0fae0; border-left: 15px solid #33FF66; margin-bottom: 20px; width: 100%; padding: 4px 10px; line-height: 1.1em; width: auto;\"><i><b>Version <a href=\"/0.31\" title=\"0.31\">0.31</a></b>: This article <b>may not be</b> up to date for the <a href=\"/0.32\" title=\"0.32\">latest stable release</a> of Crawl.</i></div>\n<table style=\"background:#f5faff; border:1px solid #cedff2; width:auto; margin: 0px 5%; margin-bottom:1.25em; font-style:italic; text-align:left; color:#000; padding:1.5em 1em;\">\n\n<tr>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 100%;\"> A glaive commissioned several years ago by a wealthy queen fearful for the safety of her vast treasury. No foe, the smith promised, could defeat a guard wielding such a weapon!\n<p>It was stolen a few months later, along with the rest of the queen's treasury; the guard, it transpired, had been caught napping. Still, it would serve more than adequately in hands of a waking user.\n</p>\n</td></tr></table>\n<p><a href=\"/File:Glaive_of_the_guard.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Glaive of the guard.png\" src=\"/images/6/6a/Glaive_of_the_guard.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a> <i><b>the +5 glaive of the Guard</b></i>\n</p><p>+5 <a href=\"/Glaive\" title=\"Glaive\">glaive</a><br />\n<a href=\"/Electrocution\" title=\"Electrocution\">Electrocution</a> brand<br />\n<a href=\"/Spectral_(brand)\" title=\"Spectral (brand)\">Spectral</a> brand<br />\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Desirability\">Desirability</span></h2>\n<p>The <b>glaive of the Guard</b><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> combines two great brands, electrocution and spectral, into one weapon. Assuming the spectral brand has room to activate, this unrand is about as strong as a +9 <a href=\"/Bardiche\" title=\"Bardiche\">bardiche</a> of <a href=\"/Flaming\" title=\"Flaming\">flaming</a>/<a href=\"/Freezing\" title=\"Freezing\">freezing</a>, but takes less skill to reach mindelay. However, it comes with the <a href=\"/Spectral_(brand)#Strategy\" title=\"Spectral (brand)\">usual risks</a> of the spectral brand.\n</p><p>Note that the spectral weapon itself does not get electrocution.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span></h2>\n<ul><li>Prior to <a href=\"/0.31\" title=\"0.31\">0.31</a>, the glaive of the Guard also gave +5 AC.</li>\n<li>Prior to <a href=\"/0.29\" title=\"0.29\">0.29</a>, the glaive of the Guard had a +8 enchantment. </li>\n<li>Prior to <a href=\"/0.26\" title=\"0.26\">0.26</a>, the glaive of the Guard did not have the <a href=\"/Spectral\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Spectral\">spectral</a> brand, but provided <a href=\"/See_invisible\" title=\"See invisible\">see invisible</a> and an <a href=\"/Berserk\" title=\"Berserk\">evocable rage</a>.</li>\n<li>Prior to <a href=\"/0.15\" title=\"0.15\">0.15</a>, the glaive of the Guard had a +5, +8 enchantment level.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span></h2>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/crawl/crawl/blob/0.29.1/crawl-ref/source/art-data.txt#L511\">art-data.txt:511</a> (0.29.1)</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20240916152153\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\n[SMW] In‐text annotation parser time: 0.006 seconds\nCPU time usage: 0.120 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.205 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 57/100000